WEBVTT

01:35.900 --> 01:40.980
=Love Beyond the Grave=
(Adapted from the novel by Li Qingran)

01:41.260 --> 01:43.990
=Episode 21=

01:54.300 --> 01:55.390
Your favorite cilantro.

01:56.300 --> 01:57.309
I don't understand why

01:57.320 --> 01:58.190
you'd like that taste.

02:01.030 --> 02:01.870
It smells so good.

02:04.990 --> 02:05.830
You don't like it?

02:16.580 --> 02:17.420
Simu,

02:17.950 --> 02:19.700
didn't we agree to live as mortals?

02:20.550 --> 02:21.460
No spirit power.

02:25.790 --> 02:26.630
Come on, eat.

02:38.350 --> 02:39.190
Simu,

02:39.950 --> 02:41.443
the 17 Prefectures have been restored,

02:42.550 --> 02:43.916
and you're no longer the Sovereign.

02:44.420 --> 02:45.260
In the future,

02:45.990 --> 02:47.070
we'll settle here,

02:47.420 --> 02:48.260
okay?

02:49.550 --> 02:50.390
Okay.

03:19.580 --> 03:20.580
A life like this

03:21.510 --> 03:22.460
might not be so bad.

03:26.790 --> 03:27.630
Duan Shunxi,

03:29.230 --> 03:30.550
I like being with you.

03:39.350 --> 03:40.190
Have some more.

03:44.510 --> 03:45.350
Hot.

03:47.860 --> 03:48.700
Come on, try it.

03:48.700 --> 03:49.570
How is it?

03:58.460 --> 03:59.300
You don't like it?

04:01.350 --> 04:02.420
I even found this.

04:03.990 --> 04:04.860
Celery leaves,

04:05.300 --> 04:06.140
pine nut crisps,

04:06.140 --> 04:07.550
sesame crisps, and rock sugar.

04:07.550 --> 04:08.390
So delicious.

04:08.580 --> 04:09.580
How can you not taste it?

04:10.140 --> 04:11.070
Next time, I'll just...

04:11.070 --> 04:11.920
Don't.

04:11.930 --> 04:12.770
No next time.

04:13.420 --> 04:14.260
Please spare me.

04:19.860 --> 04:20.982
Eat the one you already bit

04:20.993 --> 04:21.590
in your hand.

04:24.380 --> 04:25.300
Eat it.

04:34.550 --> 04:35.390
Is it good?

04:52.470 --> 04:53.380
Are you mad?

04:59.350 --> 05:00.500
You don't want to talk to me?

05:00.500 --> 05:03.300
♪Spring comes; ice and snow thaw♪

05:03.420 --> 05:04.260
Apologize.

05:06.260 --> 05:07.590
But I did nothing wrong.

05:07.590 --> 05:08.860
It took me all afternoon.

05:10.860 --> 05:11.940
Honestly.

05:14.710 --> 05:16.010
Can't you let me have this once?

05:20.670 --> 05:21.670
Alright.

05:22.710 --> 05:24.030
I won't force you to eat

05:24.030 --> 05:25.260
something you don't want.

05:30.500 --> 05:31.350
That's more like it.

05:31.350 --> 05:34.590
♪Borrow mortal warmth♪

05:34.620 --> 05:35.706
Let's go view the full moon

05:36.470 --> 05:37.380
at Mid-Autumn.

05:38.300 --> 05:39.470
In the Void, all spirits wail.

05:40.350 --> 05:42.016
You've never truly admired
the full moon.

05:43.710 --> 05:45.380
We're just making up like this?

05:45.990 --> 05:46.830
So easily?

05:48.940 --> 05:50.590
I'm very easy to appease.

05:53.010 --> 06:01.090
♪With light, carefree words,
still shining bright♪

06:02.560 --> 06:07.640
♪A pot of wine in fleeting dreams♪

06:09.370 --> 06:17.710
♪A brief life dares seek eternity♪

06:18.180 --> 06:19.740
The fruit sold quite well today.

06:21.150 --> 06:22.550
My long walk was worth it.

06:22.550 --> 06:25.540
♪Let me savor this fleeting joy♪

06:25.780 --> 06:33.040
♪May I roam drunk in dreams
and never forget♪

06:33.040 --> 06:40.240
♪Please ferry me once through this life♪

06:40.590 --> 06:41.940
Don't you love going to war?

06:43.060 --> 06:44.110
No fear of death?

06:46.060 --> 06:47.150
Now, you deserve

06:48.590 --> 06:49.430
all these wounds.

06:54.420 --> 06:55.260
Thank you.

07:00.300 --> 07:01.140
Hold me.

07:13.860 --> 07:14.700
Foxy,

07:16.060 --> 07:17.453
I won't let anything happen to you.

07:18.180 --> 07:19.020
Do you hear me?

07:38.710 --> 07:40.350
I was too selfish.

07:41.910 --> 07:43.150
I kept you by my side

07:44.500 --> 07:45.940
in the Mortal World.

07:47.350 --> 07:48.470
It must have been painful.

07:50.500 --> 07:52.030
I like staying by your side.

07:53.790 --> 07:55.420
I like being with you.

07:56.060 --> 07:57.740
These were my happiest days.

08:00.710 --> 08:01.550
You were born

08:04.260 --> 08:05.150
before I was.

08:06.420 --> 08:07.380
You stayed the same,

08:08.500 --> 08:09.350
while I'd grown old.

08:12.180 --> 08:13.230
I only regret

08:15.740 --> 08:16.940
that I couldn't

08:19.550 --> 08:20.390
stay…

08:31.380 --> 08:32.430
Simu, stop.

08:34.310 --> 08:35.260
I won't

08:36.380 --> 08:37.660
leave you on your own.

08:38.430 --> 08:40.020
I won't leave you

08:40.860 --> 08:41.700
all alone.

08:43.710 --> 08:44.550
Foxy,

08:45.140 --> 08:45.980
it's alright.

08:46.900 --> 08:47.740
It's alright.

09:03.310 --> 09:04.150
It's alright.

09:06.260 --> 09:07.430
You don't have to live in pain

09:07.430 --> 09:08.470
for me anymore.

09:13.590 --> 09:15.070
You can leave in peace now.

09:19.380 --> 09:20.230
Simu,

09:23.430 --> 09:24.470
I'm sorry.

09:27.710 --> 09:28.660
Duan Shunxi,

09:31.540 --> 09:33.260
you've already done more than enough.

09:36.310 --> 09:37.190
Truly.

09:39.110 --> 09:40.740
Thank you for staying by my side.

09:58.380 --> 09:59.220
Duan Xu.

10:05.990 --> 10:07.020
Foxy.

10:10.380 --> 10:11.310
Duan Shunxi.

10:13.830 --> 10:14.740
Duan Shunxi,

10:15.740 --> 10:17.660
I take back what I said just now.

10:17.660 --> 10:19.070
Please don't go.

10:19.590 --> 10:20.500
Please.

10:22.070 --> 10:23.740
Please don't leave me behind.

10:24.710 --> 10:25.780
Duan Shunxi,

10:27.260 --> 10:28.780
please don't go.

10:31.710 --> 10:34.230
I take back what I said just now.

10:35.430 --> 10:37.260
Don't go.

11:23.860 --> 11:26.140
All things in this world fade fast.

11:28.620 --> 11:29.590
I'm the only undying

11:31.990 --> 11:33.230
and unending one.

12:14.070 --> 12:15.020
Foxy.

12:31.990 --> 12:32.830
Duan Xu.

12:33.380 --> 12:34.220
Duan Xu,

12:35.050 --> 12:35.900
wake up.

12:35.900 --> 12:36.740
Duan Xu.

12:37.230 --> 12:38.070
Duan Xu.

12:49.740 --> 12:50.580
Simu.

12:56.110 --> 12:56.950
Simu.

12:59.660 --> 13:00.500
It's me.

13:34.140 --> 13:35.860
I'm holding your heart again.

13:44.230 --> 13:45.070
How nice.

13:47.740 --> 13:49.190
He Simu came to take me home.

13:50.950 --> 13:52.740
This is the first time in my life

13:56.740 --> 13:57.950
that someone has come for me.

14:39.190 --> 14:40.830
Jiang Ai, what are you after?

14:41.283 --> 14:42.943
Why did that mortal
lose the soul candle?

14:43.830 --> 14:45.830
Are you in league with Bai Sanxing?

14:45.923 --> 14:47.135
What you should worry about now

14:47.146 --> 14:48.339
is if Her Grace won't appear,

14:48.350 --> 14:49.070
how are we to deal

14:49.081 --> 14:49.910
with the other Lords?

14:50.710 --> 14:52.172
If anything has happened to He Simu,

14:52.183 --> 14:53.190
I will never let you off.

15:16.950 --> 15:18.540
Simu actually split the soul candle

15:18.540 --> 15:19.990
and rekindled it for Duan Xu.

15:27.420 --> 15:30.620
(Zhaomu Pavilion, the Void)

16:05.830 --> 16:06.670
Duan Xu.

16:09.830 --> 16:11.140
Can you hear me?

16:36.620 --> 16:37.853
What did you see in your dream?

17:16.150 --> 17:17.190
Foxy,

17:18.430 --> 17:19.950
I don't like seeing you like this.

17:23.670 --> 17:24.780
Wake up, please.

18:01.740 --> 18:03.710
Yan, Yan.

18:04.430 --> 18:06.540
Yan, with you in the Void,

18:07.150 --> 18:09.060
I can stay longer in the Mortal World.

18:28.100 --> 18:28.940
Don't move.

18:29.100 --> 18:30.593
You've drained too much spirit power.

18:46.630 --> 18:48.150
He is no mere mortal.

18:48.390 --> 18:49.540
He is my spell bearer.

18:49.540 --> 18:50.630
He belongs to me.

18:51.430 --> 18:52.390
I want him alive.

18:52.990 --> 18:54.020
So, he will not die.

19:08.856 --> 19:10.245
This morning assembly is being held

19:10.256 --> 19:12.260
outside Her Grace's bedchamber.

19:12.910 --> 19:14.500
This is unprecedented.

19:15.100 --> 19:16.780
Desire has clouded judgment.

19:18.910 --> 19:19.910
At this early hour,

19:19.910 --> 19:20.780
we received word

19:20.780 --> 19:22.580
from Her Grace to change the venue.

19:23.500 --> 19:24.340
What happened?

19:24.740 --> 19:26.260
It must involve that mortal.

19:30.670 --> 19:31.990
The Right Hand can bear this?

19:42.060 --> 19:42.986
The Right Hand is here.

19:43.740 --> 19:46.740
- Your Lordship.
- Your Lordship.

19:57.780 --> 19:58.960
Why hasn't the Left Hand come?

19:59.500 --> 20:01.230
It may also involve that mortal.

20:16.260 --> 20:17.100
Your Grace,

20:17.230 --> 20:18.580
all Lords are here.

20:27.260 --> 20:28.740
Lately, you've been working hard

20:28.740 --> 20:30.670
on the spirit ascension,

20:31.950 --> 20:33.950
but some, to carry out the decree,

20:34.260 --> 20:35.390
falsified the register.

20:37.430 --> 20:38.820
Please calm your anger, Your Grace.

20:39.190 --> 20:40.500
Your Grace, please forgive us.

20:41.100 --> 20:42.740
The Right Hand
has punished this already.

20:43.630 --> 20:44.820
I will not pursue it further.

21:02.950 --> 21:03.910
Those with other motives

21:04.263 --> 21:05.190
will face annihilation.

21:05.630 --> 21:06.976
If there is nothing more, dismiss.

21:07.990 --> 21:09.470
- Yes.
- Yes.

21:09.470 --> 21:10.500
Let's go.

21:25.300 --> 21:26.140
Your Grace,

21:26.470 --> 21:27.470
I ask for an audience.

21:34.540 --> 21:35.380
Speak outside.

21:37.060 --> 21:38.630
That mortal is in your bedchamber?

21:41.190 --> 21:42.260
None of your business.

21:43.400 --> 21:44.260
So, Your Grace,

21:44.260 --> 21:45.470
it was because of that mortal

21:45.470 --> 21:47.300
that today's venue was changed.

21:48.340 --> 21:49.780
Are you questioning me?

21:50.190 --> 21:51.100
I wouldn't dare.

21:51.900 --> 21:52.780
But that mortal broke

21:52.780 --> 21:54.190
into the Nine-Square Maze Prison.

21:54.470 --> 21:55.500
He also preoccupies you,

21:55.820 --> 21:57.060
making others think

21:57.060 --> 21:58.260
you're indulging in pleasure

21:58.336 --> 21:59.356
and neglecting governance.

21:59.540 --> 22:00.500
Today,

22:00.990 --> 22:02.710
the Lords have voiced complaints.

22:03.150 --> 22:04.260
If this goes on,

22:04.710 --> 22:05.710
the outcome will be dire.

22:06.150 --> 22:07.300
If they are dissatisfied,

22:07.910 --> 22:08.990
just kill them.

22:09.780 --> 22:10.620
Yan Ke,

22:11.540 --> 22:12.820
is it that they are dissatisfied,

22:12.820 --> 22:13.870
or is it you?

22:14.260 --> 22:15.100
Simu,

22:15.340 --> 22:16.670
you know I meant no such thing.

22:17.230 --> 22:18.670
I have your best interest at heart.

22:18.820 --> 22:20.230
- I…
- As the mere Right Hand,

22:20.540 --> 22:21.910
just stick to your duties.

22:22.390 --> 22:23.870
Do not overstep.

22:31.100 --> 22:32.780
The moment he set foot in the Void,

22:32.780 --> 22:33.620
he deserved to die.

22:37.260 --> 22:38.500
To protect your authority,

22:39.060 --> 22:40.390
allow me this one overstep.

22:51.470 --> 22:52.670
Let this be the last time.

23:08.100 --> 23:09.150
As the mere Right Hand,

23:09.780 --> 23:11.150
just stick to your duties.

23:11.780 --> 23:13.150
Do not overstep.

23:13.630 --> 23:15.580
The mere Right Hand?

23:16.990 --> 23:18.630
The mere Right Hand...

23:19.230 --> 23:20.150
So, in your heart,

23:20.150 --> 23:21.710
I am only your Right Hand.

24:21.740 --> 24:22.580
Don't move.

24:23.260 --> 24:24.646
You've spent too much spirit power.

24:26.790 --> 24:27.306
Don't move.

24:27.317 --> 24:28.797
You've drained too much spirit power.

24:32.630 --> 24:33.470
Simu,

24:34.300 --> 24:35.140
thank you.

25:03.470 --> 25:04.310
Yan.

25:19.540 --> 25:20.540
How dare you?

25:27.540 --> 25:28.500
Please, forgive me.

25:30.020 --> 25:31.950
Just do what I told you to do.

25:32.910 --> 25:35.390
Stop defying me at every turn.

25:53.190 --> 25:54.030
Simu,

25:55.020 --> 25:55.860
thank you.

26:18.300 --> 26:19.670
If I wanted to kiss you now,

26:22.190 --> 26:23.260
would you allow it?

26:25.630 --> 26:26.470
Bite me.

27:29.670 --> 27:30.510
What's wrong?

27:38.190 --> 27:39.030
Duan Xu.

27:40.820 --> 27:41.660
Duan Xu?

28:12.580 --> 28:13.420
How bold of you.

28:13.580 --> 28:14.990
You defied the Golden-wall Decrees

28:14.990 --> 28:16.390
and fled to torment mortals.

28:17.150 --> 28:17.990
Seize her.

28:46.950 --> 28:47.790
Your Lordship.

28:52.870 --> 28:54.820
Yan Zhang of Xuling Temple.

28:56.060 --> 28:57.430
You defied orders time and again

28:58.150 --> 28:59.260
to go to the Mortal World

28:59.260 --> 29:01.230
for one mortal man.

29:02.430 --> 29:03.270
Was it worth it?

29:04.950 --> 29:06.190
Destroy me if you must.

29:06.500 --> 29:07.740
As long as my body endures,

29:08.020 --> 29:09.540
I will go back out again.

29:13.260 --> 29:15.190
He is only a tiny mortal.

29:16.190 --> 29:18.390
You were never meant to be together.

29:19.430 --> 29:20.740
He betrayed me.

29:21.470 --> 29:22.950
I will never spare him.

29:23.780 --> 29:25.260
As long as my body remains,

29:25.950 --> 29:27.230
my hatred for him

29:27.740 --> 29:29.340
will never fade.

29:32.190 --> 29:33.500
What do you intend to do to him?

29:38.020 --> 29:39.990
What do I intend to do to him?

29:41.870 --> 29:44.060
I will flay him and break his bones.

29:45.060 --> 29:46.950
I will make him wish for life,

29:47.100 --> 29:48.430
yet never find release in death.

29:50.230 --> 29:52.230
Even if I face annihilation

29:52.580 --> 29:53.780
with arrows through my heart,

29:54.500 --> 29:55.780
I will never regret it.

30:08.780 --> 30:09.710
In that case,

30:11.230 --> 30:13.470
hand this man over to me.

30:14.540 --> 30:15.380
What do you think?

30:24.990 --> 30:26.540
It shall be as you wish.

30:42.390 --> 30:43.359
This is the jade pendant

30:43.370 --> 30:44.500
I once gave to that man.

30:45.780 --> 30:46.710
What did you do to him?

30:47.430 --> 30:48.820
He was cut down piece by piece

30:49.340 --> 30:50.740
and met a slow, agonizing end.

30:54.060 --> 30:54.950
A slow,

30:55.870 --> 30:56.820
agonizing end?

31:01.820 --> 31:02.670
Good.

31:05.740 --> 31:06.580
Well done.

31:09.060 --> 31:10.870
My vengeance is fulfilled.

31:14.670 --> 31:15.710
Good riddance.

31:22.430 --> 31:23.870
How did you evade the decrees

31:23.870 --> 31:24.710
and manage it?

31:25.910 --> 31:27.150
You can't take revenge,

31:27.950 --> 31:29.780
not because the rules forbid it,

31:30.260 --> 31:32.260
but because you're not powerful enough.

31:40.260 --> 31:41.230
I'm not powerful enough?

31:48.910 --> 31:51.190
As long as you hold enough power,

31:52.190 --> 31:53.950
you can have

31:55.990 --> 31:58.260
everything you desire.

33:24.670 --> 33:25.650
Your Grace, don't worry.

33:26.470 --> 33:27.950
He is just feverish.

33:28.630 --> 33:30.390
Once he absorbs
Ice Jade's spiritual energy,

33:30.670 --> 33:31.950
the heat toxin will fade.

33:35.300 --> 33:36.780
Do you want to save Bai Sanxing?

33:39.540 --> 33:40.520
Please, calm your wrath.

33:40.710 --> 33:42.190
I was led astray for a moment.

33:42.540 --> 33:43.630
I never meant to harm

33:43.630 --> 33:44.470
Mr. Duan.

33:46.100 --> 33:46.940
For a moment?

33:48.020 --> 33:49.580
I'd say this was planned long ago.

33:52.740 --> 33:54.670
Still, it's good you had the nerve.

33:55.330 --> 33:56.643
Otherwise, I'd never have let you

33:56.654 --> 33:57.563
serve as my Left Hand.

33:58.950 --> 33:59.790
Remember:

34:00.740 --> 34:01.866
There won't be a next time.

34:03.150 --> 34:03.990
You may rise.

34:28.830 --> 34:29.670
That child

34:30.100 --> 34:31.430
truly tugs at one's heart.

34:32.310 --> 34:33.220
When he has nightmares,

34:33.220 --> 34:34.950
he does not even cry for help.

34:38.220 --> 34:39.390
In the Prison,

34:39.390 --> 34:41.430
even when the soul candle was cut in two

34:41.620 --> 34:42.460
and went out,

34:42.620 --> 34:43.750
he was still telling me

34:44.270 --> 34:45.540
that if he made it out alive,

34:46.020 --> 34:47.790
I must tell him of your past.

34:48.750 --> 34:49.590
Your Grace,

34:50.270 --> 34:51.220
this child

34:51.790 --> 34:53.270
has truly fallen for you.

35:02.177 --> 35:03.923
They say ten fingers
are tied to the heart.

35:07.060 --> 35:08.660
Does that mean I'm holding your heart?

35:12.140 --> 35:13.270
So, this was why

35:13.270 --> 35:14.110
he fell for me?

35:19.050 --> 35:22.760
♪Falling down like snow♪

35:23.230 --> 35:26.710
♪Joys and sorrows of the mortal world♪

35:28.270 --> 35:29.610
The fingers are tied to the heart.

35:31.000 --> 35:34.800
♪The forms and hues of the mortal realm♪

35:36.270 --> 35:37.620
He entered the Prison

35:37.620 --> 35:38.660
to get to know you

35:39.180 --> 35:40.540
and to share your burdens.

35:41.750 --> 35:42.660
From what I can see,

35:43.060 --> 35:44.470
you were not untouched.

35:45.140 --> 35:47.060
Your concern and indulgence for him

35:47.263 --> 35:48.689
go far beyond those for anyone else.

35:49.580 --> 35:50.420
Simu,

35:51.950 --> 35:53.100
you have feelings for him.

35:53.620 --> 35:57.120
♪Dawn and dusk rise and set♪

35:57.390 --> 36:00.920
♪Longing to meet, yet parted by destiny♪

36:01.430 --> 36:05.040
♪Let me wander through♪

36:05.040 --> 36:08.680
♪Light and dark, without turning back♪

36:09.090 --> 36:12.490
♪Wander to the other shore
with the lantern♪

36:12.620 --> 36:16.620
♪Accompanied by eternity♪

36:16.830 --> 36:19.520
♪As all things turn and flow♪

36:19.640 --> 36:25.550
♪Whether I stay or go, I'm all alone♪

36:39.720 --> 36:43.360
♪As stars shift and change places♪

36:43.540 --> 36:47.340
♪A century is like a dream♪

36:47.570 --> 36:50.970
♪Let me journey across them all♪

36:51.160 --> 36:54.950
♪Without reincarnations♪

36:55.220 --> 36:58.830
♪A lone lamp shines on the other shore♪

36:58.830 --> 37:00.550
♪Accompanied by the abyss♪

37:00.580 --> 37:01.500
Duan Shunxi.

37:02.790 --> 37:05.600
♪Moments may last♪

37:07.470 --> 37:08.350
It truly feels

37:08.350 --> 37:09.620
like you've gripped my heart.

37:28.240 --> 37:33.570
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

37:33.900 --> 37:38.150
♪Light encountered shadow♪

37:39.510 --> 37:44.880
♪It pierced the darkness and the time♪

37:45.180 --> 37:49.780
♪The unbreakable fate♪

37:50.870 --> 37:52.710
♪Suddenly cracked♪

38:04.920 --> 38:10.360
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

38:10.540 --> 38:14.870
♪Light encountered shadow♪

38:16.240 --> 38:21.630
♪It pierced the darkness and the time♪

38:21.860 --> 38:25.800
♪The unbreakable fate♪

38:27.570 --> 38:29.460
♪Suddenly cracked♪

38:32.120 --> 38:35.280
♪Listen, all sounds are roaring♪

38:35.280 --> 38:37.810
♪As cold ice turns into tides♪

38:37.810 --> 38:43.330
♪A century's loneliness melts dreams♪

38:43.330 --> 38:46.570
♪Following fate's guidance♪

38:46.570 --> 38:51.430
♪By fate, our moments were exchanged♪

38:51.770 --> 38:54.790
♪The heart wakes up all of a sudden♪

38:54.790 --> 38:57.610
♪Watch fireworks fall like stars♪

38:57.870 --> 39:00.400
♪This bond is tangled into a thread♪

39:00.400 --> 39:05.820
♪Worldly reflections fade into mist♪

39:05.990 --> 39:09.060
♪Borrowing one fleeting heartbeat♪

39:09.220 --> 39:14.120
♪You drew me into mortal dust,
till I'm enamored with its charms♪

39:14.330 --> 39:17.800
♪The heart wakes up all of a sudden♪
